        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The scheme provides **financial loan assistance** to students from the **unreserved category** to pursue **higher education abroad.** Loans up to **₹15 lakh** are granted at simple interest of **4% per annum**, with flexible repayment options. Security and repayment conditions depend on the loan amount. This scheme aims to support meritorious, economically weaker students for global education opportunities.\n",
        "benefits_md": "**Loan Amount:** Up to ₹15.00 lakh\n**Interest Rate:** Simple interest at 4% per annum\n**Collateral:**\n**Up to ₹7.50 lakh:** Property valued at 1.5 times the loan amount\n**Above ₹7.50 lakh:** Property equal to the loan amount\n**Loan Repayment:**\n**Up to ₹5 lakh:** repay in 5 years after 1-year moratorium\n**Above ₹5 lakh**: repay in 6 years after 1-year moratorium\n<br>\n\n**Borrower can pre-pay without penalty**\n",
        "briefDescription": "Loan scheme offering up to ₹15 lakh at 4% simple interest to unreserved category students for MBBS, PG, or equivalent courses abroad with flexible collateral and repayment conditions.",
