          "process_md": "\n1. Visit the Official Website:[ **https://gueedc.gujarat.gov.in**](https://gueedc.gujarat.gov.in)1. Click on “**Register**” and fill in your basic details such as name, email, mobile number, and create a password.1. **Login** to Your Account.1.  From the dashboard, select the “**Foreign Study Loan**” scheme .1. Fill the Online Application Form.\n1. Upload Required Documents.\n1. Submit the Application.\n1.  Save or note down your **unique application ID** for future reference.1. Print the Application Form.\n1. Submit the signed hard copy and original documents for verification **at the GUEEDC office or as directed**.\n"
