      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant must be a **citizen of India** and a **resident of Gujarat.**1. The applicant must belong to the **Unreserved category**.1. The applicant must have passed **Class 12 with 60% or more marks**.1. The applicant must be seeking admission to **MBBS, Master’s, PG Diploma, or equivalent programs abroad.**1. The applicant’s annual family income must be **₹6.00 lakh or less.**\n",
